Here,  iSLOT denotes a person-level parameter,  zSLOT

   > ik
   > is a region-level parameter for the chosen

region, and  ikSLOT captures any unexplained remaining effects.

   > r

   Let xikSLOT denote the actual net revenue to the casino from player i
   wagering in slots during the

   k’th trip in region zik. Within our notation, xikSLOT > 0 indicates
