   xikSLOT < 0 indicates that the casino loses money. Following Equation
   [9], the total trip-level expected

amount that the player wins/loses in slots machines is:

E ( xikSLOT | yikSLOT , rikSLOT )  yikSLOT rikSLOT , [13]

   where yikSLOT is the amount wagered on slots and rikSLOT is the
