   SE

The purpose of the grant is to continue this well-established voter
mobilization

   >campaign beyond the EU elections on May 25th and also mobilize voters
   for
   >equality, diversity and openness and against xenophobia and
   nationalism in the
   >Swedish National elections on September 14th.

