   Tesla with written notice on May 31, 2018, that Tesla had materially
   breached the parties'

   Agreements by failing "to properly maintain and inspect the solar
   energy generation systems."

   Walmart noted that, "given the fact that the causes of the fires remain
   under investigation and in

   light of the inadequacy of Tesla's solar system inspection regimen,
   Tesla's breach has resulted in

   the creation of a significant safety hazard ... , putting Walmart's
   customers, employees,

   facilities and merchandise all at risk. Indeed, Walmart emphasizes the
