Walmart's May 31, 2018 notice of breach is attached as Exhibit 245.

   75. On June 1, 2018, Tesla responded to Walmart's letter, denying that
   it had

   breached any of the Agreements but "agree[ing] it would be prudent to
   de-energize, inspect and

