   and videos.
   >The goal is contributing to the political mobilization of the pro-EU
   voters via public
   >analyses, by two interconnected tools: a) emphasizing the stake of
   EP-elections
   >and the importance of EP as a political body and by b) alarming with
   the
   >expansion of the ethnocentric far-right and euroreject political
   forces.

